{"tid":545751,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"道具銀紙案辯方質疑：陰司紙都係假銀紙?　控方：陰司紙僅可在陰間流通","createTime":"2018-01-30T22:25:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-31T18:50:50.000Z","uid":111253,"like":85,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"4702698007672cf56ef4fe30d495e0af67b0c62b","tid":545751,"uid":111253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T22:25:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180130/57772798\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180130%2F57772798&d=j76Mz%2BdMnwm4dtScG9oTMv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=a25dc87a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180130%2F57772798&h=cb2da01a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180130/57772798</a><br />\n<br />\n金像電影《樹大招風》道具領班因管有23萬張拍戲時用的道具鈔票，被控保管偽製紙幣罪，同案另有一名向他的公司借近一萬張道具鈔票拍片的日本貨代購員。道具領班張偉全下午接受盤問時強調，該批道具鈔票並非偽鈔，辯方大狀更指「唔係真銀紙就一定係假銀紙?陰司紙都係假銀紙?」控方反駁指陰司紙僅可在陰間流通。<br />\n<br />\n張偉全承認需小心謹慎處理道具鈔票，道具鈔票若流出市面會造成很大麻煩，但他沒有道具儲存清單，每次用道具鈔票前僅是一疊一疊地數算，並非一張張地數。<br />\n<br />\n張記得2014中先拍攝《迷城》，然後再拍《樹大招風》，他否認《樹》片所用的道具鈔票是《迷》的剩餘道具，因兩片所涉不同年代。<br />\n<br />\n張指不認識首被告羅潤霖，只因羅是從事製片的女性朋友介紹，他知道羅需要道具鈔票拍微電影，而他沒有要求職員記下羅的個人資料。聆訊後天繼續。"},{"pid":"187536f4616a3f73f467f4256a0a775c75ff8485","tid":545751,"uid":111253,"like":208,"dislike":2,"score":206,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T22:26:33.000Z","msg":"控方係咪傻撚咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a21fbbb468b8516f18565e39e4c7f0067e5c51f","tid":545751,"uid":127988,"like":160,"dislike":0,"score":160,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T22:34:08.000Z","msg":"本身檢控已經on9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed0ef3e685ea0aa875f5c7a276b3d01e6de2470b","tid":545751,"uid":37666,"like":159,"dislike":0,"score":159,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T23:13:29.000Z","msg":"假銀紙夠僅可以係電影流通啦"},{"pid":"e54378d77c535f03c546ada93a264dea23a03ec6","tid":545751,"uid":8048,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T23:16:07.000Z","msg":"首先佢點知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"816fa1d37c1e5e1d3a85a6a15f8f13b019fd3441","tid":545751,"uid":135767,"like":3,"dislike":72,"score":-69,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T23:17:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fb668d57195530fb0a263507944439491032bc56","tid":545751,"uid":57376,"like":96,"dislike":2,"score":94,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T23:18:47.000Z","msg":"遲早玩大富翁要入真監獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07be3319994df85dc093f3efe69d95548c309929","tid":545751,"uid":111253,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"quote":{"pid":"e54378d77c535f03c546ada93a264dea23a03ec6","tid":545751,"uid":8048,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T23:16:07.000Z","msg":"首先佢點知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T23:20:31.000Z","msg":"落陰間採證再返陽間呈堂檢控"},{"pid":"2bd71958c268baae54c46ec66dce229017e2517a","tid":545751,"uid":50394,"like":48,"dislike":1,"score":47,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T23:22:40.000Z","msg":"係呢個痴撚線既香港，呢件事顯得好合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d824ca343ecd1e81b980583248ca0559baebfbc","tid":545751,"uid":35746,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T23:23:21.000Z","msg":"依單野都唔知做咩9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38e117cd784bcc872669baff1fca5ab27f133afd","tid":545751,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T23:37:43.000Z","msg":"弱智"},{"pid":"13cdb